---
title: Fiery Mexican Chicken & Corn Tacos  with Slaw & Spring Onion
description: Sit back and watch the fireworks display of flavour burst through these chicken tacos. They’re packed with colourful veggies like corn, carrot and garnished with spring onion and the chicken is exploding with our Mexican Fiesta spices. To cool off, drizzle over some creamy mayo.
